section.section:
The Joint Ethics Committee may exempt an individual from the provisions of paragraph (1) of this subsection if the earned income is for:
educational instruction provided by the member, candidate, or member-elect;
a position that is subject to a merit system hiring process;
a human services position; or
a career promotion, change, or progression that is a logical transition from a pre-existing relationship as described in paragraph (3)(ii) of this subsection.
